**Week Banner** — Large centered card showing pregnancy week, due date countdown, fruit-size comparison\n43\t2. **Mood Check-In Card** — Quick mood selector (5 emojis), tappable to log\n44\t3. **Today's Checklist** — Horizontal scrollable chips: weight entry, water intake, mood, symptom log\n45\t4. **Quick Actions** — 4 primary buttons: Log Weight, Log Mood, Log Symptoms, View Education\n46\t5. **Weekly Tip** — Single card with rotating wellness tip\n47\t\n48\t**Data:** Reads from `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date), `MoodEntryProvider` (today's mood), `SelfCareCheckState` (today's checklist)\n49\t\n50\t**Interactions:** Tap mood → log mood; tap weight → push weight form; tap symptom → push symptom form; tap education → tab to Education\n51\t\n52\t**Transitions:** Arrives via bottom nav tab (no animation); pull-down refreshes widget data.\n53\t\n54\t---\n55\t\n56\t### 3.2 Cycle Tracking (`/cycle-tracking`)\n57\t\n58\t**Purpose:** Log menstrual cycles, view ovulation predictions, manage cycle-related reminders.\n59\t\n60\t**Scaffold:**\n61\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Cycle Tracking\", back button\n62\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n63\t- `FAB`: `+` to log a new cycle entry\n64\t\n65\t**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n66\t\n67\t**Sections:**\n68\t1. **Current Cycle Card** — Shows days since last period, next ovulation window estimate\n69\t2. **Cycle History List** — Chronological list of logged cycles with length indicators\n70\t\n71\t**Data:** `CycleEntryProvider`\n72\t\n73\t**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet form for new cycle log; long-press history entry → edit/delete sheet; tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet\n74\t\n75\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav Browse; swipe-back to dismiss.\n76\t\n77\t---\n78\t\n79\t### 3.3 Weight & Nutrition (`/weight-nutrition`)\n80\t\n81\t**Purpose:** Log daily weight, view progress chart, read stage-specific nutrition tips.\n82\t\n83\t**Scaffold:**\n84\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Weight & Nutrition\", back button\n85\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n86\t- `FAB`: `+` to log today's weight\n87\t\n88\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n89\t\n90\t**Sections:**\n91\t1. **Progress Chart** — Line chart of weight over time; toggles 1 week / 1 month / all time\n92\t2. **Latest Entry** — Today's weight with delta from previous entry\n93\t3. **Nutrition Tips** — Stage-specific card (updates based on current pregnancy week)\n94\t4. **Weight Log List** — Scrollable list of all entries (date + weight + optional note)\n95\t\n96\t**Data:** `WeightEntryProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider` (for week-based tips)\n97\t\n98\t**Interactions:** Tap chart toggle → re-renders chart; tap `+` → bottom sheet form; long-press log entry → edit/delete sheet; tap nutrition tip → expand detail\n99\t\n100\t**Transitions:** Push from Home Browse tab or Education detail; swipe-back to dismiss.\n101\t\n102\t---\n103\t\n104\t### 3.4 Pregnancy Progress (`/pregnancy-progress`)\n105\t\n106\t**Purpose:** Due date management, week-by-week body change descriptions, fetal development visuals.\n107\t\n108\t**Scaffold:**\n109\t- `AppBar`: Title \"My Pregnancy\", back button\n110\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n111\t- `FAB`: None\n112\t\n113\t**Body:** `PageView` with `PageController` (week-by-week swiper) + bottom summary section.\n114\t\n115\t**Sections:**\n116\t1. **Week Hero** — Full-screen illustrated card with fruit-size comparison and week number prominently displayed\n117\t2. **Body Changes** — Bulleted list of what to expect this week\n118\t3. **Baby Development** — Short paragraph on fetal development\n119\t4. **Self-Care Tips** — 3 actionable tips for this week\n120\t5. **Due Date Summary** — Bottom card showing due date, days remaining, trimester badge\n121\t\n122\t**Data:** `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date)\n123\t\n124\t**Interactions:** Swipe left/right → navigate weeks; tap self-care tip → expand to full recommendation\n125\t\n126\t**Transitions:** 