21	- **Visual Atmosphere:** Soft, warm nursery aesthetic — like a cozy sunlit room with gentle natural light
22	- **Color Mood:** Cool-warm pastels anchored by lavender with blush rose accents; serene, never clinical
23	- **Typography Character:** Rounded, friendly, modern — Google Fonts "Nunito" family; generous letter-spacing for calm readability
24	- **Motion Personality:** Gentle spring-based animations with `Curves.easeInOut`; 300–400ms standard duration; nothing abrupt or bouncy
